       01  WRK-OPCAO-MENU              PIC 9(002) VALUE ZEROS.        

      *================================================================*
       PROCEDURE                       DIVISION.
      *================================================================*

      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *    PROCESSAMENTO PRINCIPAL
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *> cobol-lint CL002 0000-processar
       0000-PROCESSAR                  SECTION.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*

           PERFORM 0001-MENU-INICIAL 
           .
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *> cobol-lint CL002 0000-end
       0000-END.                       EXIT.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*


      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *    TELA MENU INICIAL
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
       0001-MENU-INICIAL                  SECTION.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*

           INITIALIZE WRK-OPCAO-MENU 

           DISPLAY '*=====================================*'
           DISPLAY '*         SISTEMA COBOL DICAS         *'
           DISPLAY '*-------------------------------------*'
           DISPLAY '* 1 - CADASTRAR CLIENTES              *'
           DISPLAY '* 2 - LISTA CLIENTES                  *'
           DISPLAY '* 3 - SAIR                            *'
           DISPLAY '*                                     *'
           DISPLAY '* ESCOLHA UM OPCAO : '
           WITH NO ADVANCING
           ACCEPT WRK-OPCAO-MENU 
           DISPLAY '*                                     *'
           DISPLAY '*=====================================*'
           
           EVALUATE WRK-OPCAO-MENU
            WHEN 1
                PERFORM 0002-CADASTRAR-CLIENTE
            WHEN 2
                PERFORM 0003-LISTAR-CLIENTE 
            WHEN 3
                PERFORM 9999-FINALIZAR
            WHEN OTHER
                DISPLAY 'OPCAO INVALIDA!'
                PERFORM 0001-MENU-INICIAL
           END-EVALUATE
           .
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *> cobol-lint CL002 0001-end
       0001-END.                       EXIT.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*

      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *    CADASTRO DE CLIENTES
