           DISPLAY '*-------------------------------------*'

           CALL 'PROG034A'
           .
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *> cobol-lint CL002 0002-end
       0002-END.                       EXIT.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*


      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
