       0003-END.                       EXIT.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*

      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *    FINALIZAR PROGRAMA
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *> cobol-lint CL002 9999-finalizar
       9999-FINALIZAR                  SECTION.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
           DISPLAY 'FIM DE PROGRAMA'
           STOP RUN 
           .           
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
